<div class="container">
  <div class="box">
    <img src="http://mishalandsamuel.com/logo.png">
    <p>Here's an updated copy of the master CSV. Here's also some overview stats of your guests:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Total Unconfirmed Guests:</strong> <%= Guest.where(:response => 0).count %></li>
      <li><strong>Total RSVP'd Guests:</strong> <%= Guest.all.count - Guest.where(:response => 0).count %></li>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Total Not Attending Guests:</strong> <%= Guest.where(:response => 2).count %></li>
        <li><strong>Total Attending Guests:</strong> <%= Guest.where(:response => 1).count %></li>
        <ul>
          <% Meal.all.find_each do |meal| %>
            <li><strong>Total <%= meal.name %> Orders:</strong> <%= Guest.where(:meal => meal).count %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </ul>
    </ul>
    <p>Let me know if you need anything else!</p>
    <p class="closing">
      <span>Thanks,</span>
      <br>
      <span>Robin</span>
    </p>
  </div>
